text: Ordered roasted chicken rice and they give me steamed chicken rice. I refused and said I wanted roasted, then they tried to convince me that steamed chicken rice is roasted because they didn't want to make another one. Waste of time.
Chicken rice was tasty, reasonably priced ($3.50) and generous in portion. Sellers were friendly, stall was clean and e-payment was available. What else to ask for?
They have chicken feet!!! So hard to find too..  the chill good and rice also very fragrant.. the soup!! So much veg and soup taste good.. very good.. will come back again.
Good and tasty. Portion is generous. $3.50 is a steal for this serving.
solid roasted and steamed chicken rice with fiery chili sauce. Hidden in 1 corner of a coffeeshop.
